<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Reminder: Pending Document Upload</title>
    <!--[if mso]>
      <xml>
        <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
          <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>
        </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
      </xml>
      <style>
        table {
          mso-table-lspace: 0pt !important;
          mso-table-rspace: 0pt !important;
        }
      </style>
    <![endif]-->
    <style>
      @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap");

      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        width: 100% !important;
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        background-color: #f1f5f9;
        font-family: "Outfit", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
          Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      }

      img {
        border: 0;
        outline: none;
        text-decoration: none;
        -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
      }

      table {
        border-collapse: collapse !important;
      }

      .wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        table-layout: fixed;
        background-color: #f1f5f9;
        padding: 40px 0;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1c3260 0%, #2a4a85 100%);
        padding: 40px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .header-icon {
        font-size: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .header-title {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        line-height: 1.3;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1e293b;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .body-text {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #475569;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .details-card {
        background-color: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }

      .details-title {
        font-size: 12px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #64748b;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        padding-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .details-row {
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .details-row:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      .details-label {
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #64748b;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .details-value {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1c3260;
      }

      .btn-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 32px 0;
      }

      .btn {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1c3260 0%, #2a4a85 100%);
        color: #ffffff !important;
        padding: 14px 32px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 15px;
        display: inline-block;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(28, 50, 96, 0.25);
      }

      .link-text {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #64748b;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 24px;
        word-break: break-all;
      }

      .link-text a {
        color: #2a4a85;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 30px;
        background-color: #f8fafc;
        border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .footer-signoff {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #475569;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .footer-signoff strong {
        color: #1c3260;
      }

      .footer-disclaimer {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: #94a3b8;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
          <div class="header-icon">📬</div>
          <h1 class="header-title">Pending Document Upload</h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
          <p class="greeting">Dear Resident,</p>

          <p class="body-text">
            This is a friendly reminder that we are still waiting for the
            required document uploads for the submission details outlined below.
          </p>

          <!-- Details Card -->
          <div class="details-card">
            <div class="details-title">Submission Details</div>

            <div class="details-row">
              <div class="details-label">Form Name</div>
              <div class="details-value"><%= formName %></div>
            </div>

            <div class="details-row" style="margin-top: 16px">
              <div class="details-label">Property</div>
              <div class="details-value"><%= propertyName %></div>
            </div>

            <div class="details-row" style="margin-top: 16px">
              <div class="details-label">Unit</div>
              <div class="details-value"><%= unitName %></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="body-text">
            To prevent any delays in processing, please click the button below
            to securely connect and complete your pending file uploads.
          </p>

          <% if (typeof uploadLink !== 'undefined' && uploadLink) { %>
          <!-- CTA Button -->
          <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="<%= uploadLink %>" class="btn"> Upload Files Now </a>
          </div>

          <p class="link-text">
            If the button above does not work, copy and paste this link into
            your browser:<br />
            <a href="<%= uploadLink %>"><%= uploadLink %></a>
          </p>
          <% } %>

          <p
            class="body-text"
            style="font-size: 14px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 32px"
          >
            If you have already uploaded these documents, you can safely ignore
            this automated reminder. Thank you for your cooperation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
          <p class="footer-signoff">
            Kind regards,<br />
            <strong>Premium Property Team</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="footer-disclaimer">
            This is an automated request portal from Premium Property. Please do
            not reply directly to this email.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
